## Environment Variables Needed

```env
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://xxx.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=xxx
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=https://civicsync.vercel.app   # backend URL
```

> Backend team will provide the `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL` once deployed.

---

## Important Rules

1. **Never call Supabase directly from frontend** for reports — always go through `/api/*` routes
2. **Map must be dynamically imported** (`ssr: false`) — Leaflet breaks with SSR
3. **Use `lib/schemas.ts`** (provided by backend) for all Zod types — do not redefine
4. **All admin routes** check for `admin_auth` cookie before rendering
5. **Commit frequently** to avoid merge conflicts — coordinate on `components/` folder
